@Bugfix update to thunderbird 17.0.7.

- Fixes MFSA 2013-49,50,51,53,54,55,56 & 59
- rework tb-i18n's MESSAGE to be more in line with reality
@
text
@To configure Thunderbird for your language, allow thunderbird to
activate the installed language at first start, open the configuration
editor (Preferences->Advanced->Config Editor) and set the
"general.useragent.locale" key to the language you want to use.
@


